      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Yes, this clause allows the supplier to automatically implement a price adjustment of up to 5% during June, July, and August. The language explicitly states these adjustments \"shall be enacted automatically at the commencement of the specified month,\" meaning no prior negotiation is required for those seasonal increases. However, this only applies to the defined peak months; any other changes must follow the mutual written amendment process.",
